        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-06-19 12:32:55.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Actually the dependency is required because mockito is being used\n > for creating mocks in the tests I have modified.\n\nI have found that including powermock automatically includes mockito, so I don't normally include mockito in the pom if powermock is already included.  Nevertheless, if it's still needed in this case, then certainly, go ahead and include it.",
