          "account_id": 2815,
          "name": "Michal Kabaj",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "michal.kabaj@nokia.com",
          "username": "kabayashi"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-06-19 12:37:57.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nOk, I understand:) My approach in this case is to have explicitly defined dependencies without relying on transitivity. Mainly because of two reasons: \n- powermock/powermockito dependencies should and are planned to be removed\n- explicit deps are more readable and allow for better version control.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
